headline: L3Harris to Produce Additional Solid Rocket Motors for Precision-Guided Artillery System
summary: MELBOURNE, Fla., December 10, 2025--L3Harris Technologies (NYSE: LHX) has been awarded a follow-on production contract valued up to $200 million to manufacture Guided Multiple Launch Rocket System (GMLRS) Insensitive Munition (IM) propulsion units.
